General.Name: Alternative Investment Trust
General.Description: Alternative Investment Trust is a balanced mutual fund launched by RE The Trust Company (RE Services) Limited. The fund is co-managed by Laxey Partners (UK) Limited and Laxey Partners Ltd. It invests in the equity and fixed income markets of Australia. The fund also invests in absolute return funds. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies that are operating across diversified sectors. The fund was formerly known as Everest Babcock & Brown Alternative Investment Trust. Alternative Investment Trust was formed on April 7, 2005 and is domiciled in Australia.
